      "id": "web_api",
      "title": "Steam Web API",
      "description": "HTTP-based API at api.steampowered.com. Format: /<interface>/<method>/v<version>/?key=<key>&format=<format>. Supports JSON (default), XML, VDF.",
      "content": {
